Kvarken Archipelago.title: Kvarken Archipelago
Kvarken Archipelago.byline: The Kvarken Archipelago (Swedish: Kvarkens skärgård, Finnish: Merenkurkun saaristo) is an archipelago in the narrowest part of the Gulf of Bothnia, between Finland and Sweden.

Kvarner.title: Kvarner
Kvarner.byline: Kvarner and Highlands is a region of Croatia including the seashore and highlands north of Dalmatia and connects Istria with the rest of Croatia.
